txt.en: 'The Circle of Madness has been completely overrun by Lhaereth's forces. We will not be able to press farther into the city until they are removed. I ask that you defeat any you come across.'
Stained merrevail have invaded Minas Morgul and taken over the Circle of Madness.
'Excellent work, [placeholder]. While this enemy is known to us, it is prudent not to let your guard down. We know full well of what they are capable.'
Stained merrevail have taken over the third tier in Minas Morgul, the Circle of Madness.\n\nYou should defeat stained merrevail.
Faeron is stationed inside Barad Elenath, the Star-gazers' Spire.\n\nYou should talk to Faeron.
